{"body": "Section 228) **Annual allowance**\n\n1) The annual allowance for the tax year 2023-24 and, subject to subsection (2), each subsequent tax year is \u00a360,000. \n2) The Treasury may by order provide that the annual allowance for any tax year subsequent to the tax year 2023-24 is such amount as is specified in the order. ", "citation_label": "2004 c. 12 s. 228", "citation_path": "uk/statute/ukpga/2004/12/228", "document_class": "statute", "expression_date": "2026-06-01-uk-frs-microsim", "heading": "Annual allowance", "id": "cc332340-eabb-5380-b8cb-eea9cc185a42", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "12", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "228", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "ukpga", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2004"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "section", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "2004 c. 12 s. 228", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": [], "references_to": [], "retrieved_at": "2026-06-01"}, "ordinal": 228, "parent_citation_path": "uk/statute/ukpga/2004/12", "parent_id": "1e041342-d1a2-56b2-87b2-5ae8dda62d86", "source_as_of": "2026-06-01-uk-frs-microsim", "source_document_id": "ukpga/2004/12", "source_format": "lex.lab.i.ai.gov.uk", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2004/12/section/228", "source_path": "sources/uk/statute/2026-06-01-uk-frs-microsim/ukpga/2004/12/section-228.json", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2004/12/section/228", "version": "2026-06-01-uk-frs-microsim"}
